  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy Study of STX209 in Subjects With Fragile X Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Crossover, Flexible-Dose Evaluation of the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of STX209 in the Treatment of Irritability in Subjects With Fragile X Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
