    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to explore the efficacy, safety and tolerability of STX209 for
      treatment of irritability in subjects with FSX. We hypothesize that STX209 will improve
      irritability and other typical problem behaviors associated with fragile X syndrome. We also
      hypothesize that STX209 will be safe and well tolerated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
